12:43.696 --> 12:45.032
HEY.

12:45.032 --> 12:47.667
I'M REALLY SORRY
ABOUT YOUR MOM, ANGIE.

12:47.667 --> 12:50.670
THANK YOU, ERNIE.

12:50.670 --> 12:52.105
YOU DOING OKAY, BABY?

12:52.105 --> 12:55.175
